  <p>Shiatsu is an energetic manual therapy that involves applying finger pressure to the body's meridians and stretching. It is based on traditional Chinese medicine and has Japanese origins.</p>
  <p>You can enjoy in your room a session provided by Nadine, trained in Chinese medicine and acupuncture. Lying on a massage table, this session will help you reduce tension, stimulate and strengthen your immune system.</p>
